com.digitalpersona.uareu

Interface Importer


  • public interface Importer
    Import interface.

    Importer allows to import images and FMDs in binary form, from existing data.

    • Method Summary

    • Method Detail

      • ImportRaw

        Fid ImportRaw(byte[] data,
            int width,
            int height,
            int dpi,
            int finger_position,
            int cbeff_id,
            Fid.Format out_format,
            int out_dpi,
            boolean rotate180)
              throws UareUException
        Imports raw image and converts it to ANSI or ISO format.

        Parameters:
        data - Image data to import.
        width - Width of the image.
        height - Height of the image.
        dpi - Resolution of the image in DPI.
        finger_position - Position of the finger.
        cbeff_id - CBEFF product ID, from IBIA registry.
        out_format - Format of the resulting FID.
        out_dpi - Resolution of the resulting FID in DPI.
        rotate180 - flag: rotate image, false - do not rotate, true - rotate.
        Returns:
        Imported FID
        Throws:
        UareUException - if failed to create FID

        Fid ImportFid(byte[] data,

        Imports image in ANSI or ISO format.

        If image is in legacy DP image format, it must be converted to ANSI or ISO image format.

        Parameters:
        data - FID data to import.
        format - Format of the FID.
        Returns:
        Imported FID
        Throws:
